1
00:00:05,920 --> 00:00:08,627
♫  I want to go to the future  ♫

2
00:00:08,627 --> 00:00:12,182
♫  Time has bear witness to my quirkiness  ♫

3
00:00:12,182 --> 00:00:18,375
♫  I want to seize the day and put the whole world into my head  ♫

4
00:00:18,375 --> 00:00:24,601
♫  I want to go back in time to do all the crazy things I didn't do  ♫

5
00:00:24,601 --> 00:00:31,020
♫  Don't say goodbye, don't be in a daze, let my radiant light be bright  ♫

6
00:00:31,020 --> 00:00:36,108
♫  We are always looking forward to the unknown future  ♫

7
00:00:36,108 --> 00:00:43,208
♫  And often overlooking our surroundings and best plan in front of us  ♫

8
00:00:43,208 --> 00:00:48,432
♫  Every day my heart beats for you  ♫

9
00:00:48,432 --> 00:00:49,860
♫  Be your light  ♫

10
00:00:49,860 --> 00:00:55,700
♫  You are no doubt irreplaceable  ♫

11
00:00:55,700 --> 00:01:02,208
♫  Every day the sun shines through the window  ♫

12
00:01:02,208 --> 00:01:08,375
♫  With the reflection of you being my incredible highlight  ♫

13
00:01:08,375 --> 00:01:11,899
[I Don't Want to be Brothers with You]

14
00:01:15,419 --> 00:01:17,879
You're making dinner again, Gao Bin?

15
00:01:17,879 --> 00:01:20,980
I'm telling you, your cooking is really inedible.

16
00:01:20,980 --> 00:01:23,640
Just cook some instant noodles.

17
00:01:26,219 --> 00:01:27,480
Smells pretty good.

18
00:01:27,480 --> 00:01:29,580
What are you making?

19
00:01:32,039 --> 00:01:33,699
You're home?

20
00:01:33,699 --> 00:01:36,340
Dinner will be ready soon.

21
00:01:36,340 --> 00:01:38,620
Why are you at my house?

22
00:01:38,620 --> 00:01:40,937
Answer me!

23
00:01:40,937 --> 00:01:42,320
Gao Yang, you're home?

24
00:01:42,320 --> 00:01:44,799
Hurry, Bin! Hurry, hurry! What's going on?

25
00:01:44,799 --> 00:01:46,012
You two know each other?

26
00:01:46,012 --> 00:01:48,059
Xiaowen, he just transferred to your class today.

27
00:01:48,059 --> 00:01:50,000
So what? Why is he at our house?

28
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:53,359
What are you yelling for? Put that down.

29
00:01:54,200 --> 00:01:55,870
Come here.

30
00:01:56,759 --> 00:01:57,940
Wait, what's going on?

31
00:01:57,940 --> 00:02:01,059
From now on, Xiaowen will be staying at our house.

32
00:02:01,059 --> 00:02:03,259
Xiaowen is an excellent boy.

33
00:02:03,259 --> 00:02:05,606
You should learn from him.

34
00:02:05,606 --> 00:02:08,539
Are... are you joking with me, Brother Bin?

35
00:02:08,539 --> 00:02:11,920
Do you think I'm joking with you?

36
00:02:13,972 --> 00:02:16,860
I'm a bit confused. Let me straighten it out.

37
00:02:16,860 --> 00:02:19,080
Wait a minute. We have a two-bedroom apartment.

38
00:02:19,080 --> 00:02:21,880
- If he's here, where should I go?
- Where else can you go?

39
00:02:21,880 --> 00:02:23,659
Stay home.

40
00:02:23,659 --> 00:02:26,000
But how will we sleep?

41
00:02:26,580 --> 00:02:29,094
That's the right question. Come on.

42
00:02:29,094 --> 00:02:31,139
Come here. Take a look.

43
00:02:31,139 --> 00:02:33,219
Wasn't this filled with litter up there?

44
00:02:33,219 --> 00:02:35,239
I cleaned it out.

45
00:02:35,239 --> 00:02:39,759
From now on, the two of you will be brothers sharing one bunk. Do you understand?

46
00:02:39,759 --> 00:02:41,939
Why should I share a bunk bed with him?

47
00:02:41,939 --> 00:02:43,659
Who wants to be his brother?

48
00:02:43,659 --> 00:02:46,059
- How is he? Who is he?
- Stop... stop yelling.

49
00:02:46,059 --> 00:02:48,580
What are you yelling for? You think you're the only one who can yell?

50
00:02:48,580 --> 00:02:51,260
Xiaowen is my friend's child.

51
00:02:51,260 --> 00:02:53,180
Something came up in his family.

52
00:02:53,180 --> 00:02:56,439
I'll explain the details to you later, okay?

53
00:02:56,439 --> 00:02:59,140
I'm going on a business trip.

54
00:02:59,140 --> 00:03:01,539
Xiaowen, come out here.

55
00:03:03,740 --> 00:03:05,040
Mr. Gao.

56
00:03:05,040 --> 00:03:07,260
Xiaowen, now that you and Gao Yang know each other,

57
00:03:07,260 --> 00:03:09,300
you two should get along with each other.

58
00:03:09,300 --> 00:03:11,380
Help me keep an eye on him.

59
00:03:11,380 --> 00:03:12,980
I'm leaving for my business trip now.

60
00:03:12,980 --> 00:03:15,025
By the way.

61
00:03:18,640 --> 00:03:20,700
You don't need to give me so much.

62
00:03:20,700 --> 00:03:22,939
One, two, three, four...

63
00:03:22,939 --> 00:03:25,869
Five hundred is too much.

64
00:03:27,099 --> 00:03:28,560
Take this.

65
00:03:28,560 --> 00:03:32,359
Gao Yang, Xiaowen will be in charge.

66
00:03:32,359 --> 00:03:35,460
But... But why are you giving it to him and not to me?

67
00:03:35,460 --> 00:03:37,999
Give you money? You don't have common sense.

68
00:03:37,999 --> 00:03:41,701
If I give you money, you'll go to Beijing as soon as I leave.

69
00:03:42,980 --> 00:03:46,900
- I'm leaving.
- Mr. Gao, have dinner before you go.

70
00:03:46,900 --> 00:03:48,860
That's all right. I have to catch the train.

71
00:03:48,860 --> 00:03:51,080
Wait, Brother Bin!

72
00:03:51,080 --> 00:03:52,700
Gao Bin!

73
00:03:52,700 --> 00:03:55,583
No, Dad! Dad! Dad!

74
00:03:59,059 --> 00:04:01,339
Dinner is almost ready.

75
00:04:08,600 --> 00:04:10,695
Winter is coming.

76
00:04:13,580 --> 00:04:15,281
Hurry, hurry.

77
00:04:15,281 --> 00:04:16,960
It's so hot.

78
00:04:16,960 --> 00:04:18,400
Mom, are there other dishes?

79
00:04:18,400 --> 00:04:21,128
- There's braised pork in brown sauce.
- Braised pork is wonderful!

80
00:04:21,128 --> 00:04:23,359
Hurry, hurry. Go ask your brother to dinner.

81
00:04:23,359 --> 00:04:26,660
Mom, he's so fat already, it's fine if he misses a meal.

82
00:04:26,660 --> 00:04:30,568
What are you talking about? Go get him.

83
00:04:30,568 --> 00:04:33,399
- Got it.
- Old Jin, stop fidgeting with your calligraphy.

84
00:04:33,399 --> 00:04:35,834
- It's time for dinner.
- Coming.

85
00:04:35,834 --> 00:04:38,460
I have to call each one of you to dinner.

86
00:04:38,460 --> 00:04:40,400
Jin Doudou, time for dinner!

87
00:04:40,400 --> 00:04:42,460
Jin Doudou, get off my bed!

88
00:04:42,460 --> 00:04:45,280
Sister, do I look good in this dress?

89
00:04:45,280 --> 00:04:49,040
Why are you wearing my dress again? Take it off! You're stretching it out!

90
00:04:49,040 --> 00:04:51,980
So what if I'm stretching it out? This dress is so old-fashioned.

91
00:04:51,980 --> 00:04:54,079
Gao Yang will definitely hate it!

92
00:04:54,079 --> 00:04:57,260
- Take if off!
- No, I won't!

93
00:04:57,260 --> 00:04:58,979
What are you two fighting about? Come and eat.

94
00:04:58,979 --> 00:05:00,399
Dad, look at him!

95
00:05:00,399 --> 00:05:01,779
Come eat dinner first.

96
00:05:01,779 --> 00:05:04,639
That's enough. Come eat dinner first.

97
00:05:07,600 --> 00:05:08,759
This piece is so big.

98
00:05:08,759 --> 00:05:10,515
Don't give him fatty pieces all the time.

99
00:05:10,515 --> 00:05:11,940
How is that fatty? It's delicious.

100
00:05:11,940 --> 00:05:13,740
This piece is leaner. Here, here.

101
00:05:13,740 --> 00:05:16,321
Eat more. You're growing up.

102
00:05:19,199 --> 00:05:21,859
What's wrong with you? Why aren't you eating?

103
00:05:21,859 --> 00:05:24,300
Why did you have to have a second child?

104
00:05:26,100 --> 00:05:30,099
Beibei, how can you say that in front of your brother?

105
00:05:30,099 --> 00:05:31,879
That's right. You're...

106
00:05:31,879 --> 00:05:35,599
He wore my dress! He almost ruined it.

107
00:05:37,339 --> 00:05:41,579
Doudou, don't mess with your sister's things anymore. Do you hear me?

108
00:05:41,579 --> 00:05:43,753
Good boy.

109
00:05:43,753 --> 00:05:46,040
I'm sorry, Sister.

110
00:05:46,040 --> 00:05:47,759
You're still putting on an act?

111
00:05:47,759 --> 00:05:52,260
If you really want to apologize, give me all the meat in your bowl.

112
00:05:57,239 --> 00:05:59,660
You see? He never wanted to apologize.

113
00:05:59,660 --> 00:06:01,400
Sister, I'll give you all of that.

114
00:06:01,400 --> 00:06:03,819
- Look!
- Look!

115
00:06:03,819 --> 00:06:05,900
Look!

116
00:06:08,820 --> 00:06:12,280
I'm sorry, Sister. I'll get you another piece.

117
00:06:12,280 --> 00:06:15,159
You did that on purpose!

118
00:06:15,159 --> 00:06:17,099
He just sneezed accidentally.

119
00:06:17,099 --> 00:06:20,319
Exactly. He already apologized to you, right?

120
00:06:20,319 --> 00:06:23,439
Fine, you guys keep eating.

121
00:06:23,980 --> 00:06:26,140
You have such a short temper! You...

122
00:06:26,140 --> 00:06:28,319
What's wrong with her?

123
00:06:42,199 --> 00:06:43,883
Let's eat.

124
00:06:53,500 --> 00:06:55,432
Why did you come to my house?

125
00:06:57,580 --> 00:06:59,580
I'm talking to you.

126
00:07:00,360 --> 00:07:02,439
I'm talking to you.

127
00:07:16,299 --> 00:07:21,579
When you sat next to me this morning, did you already know you were coming to my house tonight?

128
00:07:21,579 --> 00:07:23,014
Yes.

129
00:07:25,339 --> 00:07:28,460
Why did you deliberately plan to approach me?

130
00:07:32,099 --> 00:07:33,380
You're not saying anything?

131
00:07:33,380 --> 00:07:35,380
What's the point of not saying anything?

132
00:07:35,380 --> 00:07:37,779
Do you think you can stay in this house so easily?

133
00:07:37,779 --> 00:07:39,679
Gao Bin doesn't have the last word.

134
00:07:39,679 --> 00:07:41,879
Then, do you have the last word?

135
00:07:44,840 --> 00:07:47,900
You can go do homework if you don't want to eat.

136
00:07:47,900 --> 00:07:49,280
I can finish it all by myself.

137
00:07:49,280 --> 00:07:52,519
Why should I? Why should I let you eat it all?

138
00:08:12,339 --> 00:08:14,520
Did you really make all this?

139
00:08:14,520 --> 00:08:15,819
Yes.

140
00:08:15,819 --> 00:08:18,520
It's so awful. Only the rice is edible.

141
00:08:19,219 --> 00:08:21,299
- Don't eat it then.
- Why can't I eat them?

142
00:08:21,299 --> 00:08:24,239
This is my house. I'll eat whatever I want.

143
00:08:24,239 --> 00:08:28,336
I'm going to eat the food you made and I'm still going to be at odds with you.

144
00:08:50,240 --> 00:08:53,879
Since I ate the food you made, I'll chat with you for a little bit.

145
00:08:53,879 --> 00:08:56,160
Why must you come to my house?

146
00:08:56,160 --> 00:08:58,420
You should go to a big city.

147
00:08:58,420 --> 00:09:01,479
What's my house? It's a pit of fire, the devil's den.

148
00:09:01,479 --> 00:09:03,579
I tried to escape a few days ago and I failed.

149
00:09:03,579 --> 00:09:05,559
All right, now you're here.

150
00:09:05,559 --> 00:09:07,879
Are you stupid?

151
00:09:10,640 --> 00:09:12,520
Look at this bowl.

152
00:09:12,520 --> 00:09:14,900
Do you know why it's so white? It's new.

153
00:09:14,900 --> 00:09:16,459
Gao Bin never cooked before.

154
00:09:16,459 --> 00:09:19,094
Now you're here, you'll have to serve him.

155
00:09:22,900 --> 00:09:25,640
Do you know what kind of person Gao Bin is?

156
00:09:25,640 --> 00:09:27,539
He's known for having no ambition at all.

157
00:09:27,539 --> 00:09:30,240
All he does every day is muck around. His peer who went to school in the same year,

158
00:09:30,240 --> 00:09:31,839
Jin Beibei's dad, lives right upstairs.

159
00:09:31,839 --> 00:09:33,359
He's already the principal now.

160
00:09:33,359 --> 00:09:35,380
He is still a PE teacher.

161
00:09:35,380 --> 00:09:37,299
Besides that, he drinks heavily every day.

162
00:09:37,299 --> 00:09:40,820
If it weren't for my sake, the school would've fired him a long time ago.

163
00:09:40,820 --> 00:09:43,699
Mr. Gao isn't as bad as you say.

164
00:09:44,719 --> 00:09:47,299
Do you know him better than me?

165
00:09:47,299 --> 00:09:49,459
Don't give me that nonsense.

166
00:09:49,459 --> 00:09:51,980
Tell me, how long are you going to stay?

167
00:09:51,980 --> 00:09:53,699
You don't want me to stay here, right?

168
00:09:53,699 --> 00:09:55,640
Well, it depends on our relationship.

169
00:09:55,640 --> 00:09:59,580
If you're my friend, you can stay for as long as you want.

170
00:09:59,580 --> 00:10:01,017
Got it.

171
00:10:01,780 --> 00:10:03,625
I can leave.

172
00:10:03,625 --> 00:10:06,179
Then hurry up.

173
00:10:06,179 --> 00:10:08,155
Thank you.

174
00:10:08,779 --> 00:10:11,242
But I have to wait until Mr. Gao comes home.

175
00:10:11,980 --> 00:10:15,019
Within these few days, you have to listen to me.

176
00:10:15,019 --> 00:10:16,939
Why should I listen to you?

177
00:10:16,939 --> 00:10:19,380
I've lived here for over ten years. Why should I listen to you?

178
00:10:19,380 --> 00:10:21,219
Who do you think you are?

179
00:10:23,040 --> 00:10:24,903
I'm talking to you.

180
00:10:26,880 --> 00:10:29,872
I'll take the bottom bunk. Is that a problem?

181
00:10:36,579 --> 00:10:38,199
Do you know?

182
00:10:38,199 --> 00:10:43,179
Throughout the entire Tieyuan, no one dares to make a scene in front of me.

183
00:10:43,179 --> 00:10:45,660
Take your foot off.

184
00:10:45,660 --> 00:10:48,215
Well,

185
00:10:48,215 --> 00:10:50,635
you're so arrogant, huh?

186
00:10:51,760 --> 00:10:53,850
You're so cocky.

187
00:11:07,400 --> 00:11:08,600
You can have it all.

188
00:11:08,600 --> 00:11:10,080
Sleep wherever you want.

189
00:11:10,080 --> 00:11:13,240
Sleep on the top bunk for the first half of the night and the bottom bunk for the second half of the night.

190
00:11:13,240 --> 00:11:15,809
I'm going to Beijing soon anyway.

191
00:11:15,809 --> 00:11:19,840
These days, I'll be sleeping on Gao Bin's big bed.

192
00:11:19,840 --> 00:11:22,900
It's comfy and soft.

193
00:13:11,959 --> 00:13:14,191
Go sleep in the room.

194
00:13:25,240 --> 00:13:26,897
What are you doing?

195
00:13:29,299 --> 00:13:32,699
Go away. Psycho.

196
00:13:32,699 --> 00:13:35,460
Are you a psycho? Go sleep in the room!

197
00:13:35,460 --> 00:13:37,620
Fine, I'll sleep in the room.

198
00:13:37,620 --> 00:13:39,555
Why are you getting physical?

199
00:13:52,340 --> 00:13:54,188
I'm going to sleep.

200
00:14:40,059 --> 00:14:45,500
Fighting with me and glaring at me!

201
00:14:45,500 --> 00:14:48,700
Let me tell you, Gao Bin is my dad.

202
00:14:48,700 --> 00:14:52,079
When he comes back, he'll do whatever I tell him!

203
00:14:52,079 --> 00:14:55,679
I'll tell him to throw you out, let alone share a bunk bed with you!

204
00:14:55,679 --> 00:14:58,219
You think you're so awesome.

205
00:15:00,299 --> 00:15:02,039
The bed is so much more comfortable.

206
00:15:03,320 --> 00:15:06,280
The bed is so much more comfortable!

207
00:15:12,720 --> 00:15:14,679
Smells so good.

208
00:15:15,779 --> 00:15:17,299
Dad, you're home.

209
00:15:17,299 --> 00:15:19,500
Try some of my cooking.

210
00:15:20,779 --> 00:15:22,419
You learned to cook?

211
00:15:22,419 --> 00:15:24,900
I just learned it.

212
00:15:24,900 --> 00:15:29,040
It's too late to learn it now.

213
00:15:29,040 --> 00:15:30,880
It's not too late. I'm only seventeen.

214
00:15:30,880 --> 00:15:34,059
Gao Yang, I want to tell you something.

215
00:15:34,059 --> 00:15:37,100
You're not my son.

216
00:15:37,100 --> 00:15:39,699
I promised someone to raise you until you're 18.

217
00:15:39,699 --> 00:15:43,899
After your birthday, you should leave.

218
00:15:45,160 --> 00:15:48,539
Dad. I'm home.

219
00:15:48,539 --> 00:15:53,880
Son, is this food edible?

220
00:15:57,620 --> 00:15:59,539
What do you want to eat?

221
00:15:59,539 --> 00:16:01,960
I want to eat stew in an iron pot.

222
00:16:01,960 --> 00:16:04,260
We'll eat stew in an iron pot then.

223
00:16:04,260 --> 00:16:06,399
We'll order two pots.

224
00:16:06,399 --> 00:16:08,659
We'll eat one

225
00:16:09,779 --> 00:16:12,199
and toss the other one away.

226
00:16:13,480 --> 00:16:15,480
Why?

227
00:16:42,500 --> 00:16:44,451
Ye Xiaowen!

228
00:16:44,451 --> 00:16:46,346
Ye Xiaowen!

229
00:16:58,880 --> 00:17:01,097
I'm not messing with you guys anymore.

230
00:17:15,920 --> 00:17:17,559
Where is it?

231
00:17:27,000 --> 00:17:29,299
Did Gao Bin take it with him?

232
00:17:30,760 --> 00:17:32,786
Eternal Love and Harmony.

233
00:17:47,480 --> 00:17:50,399
Twenty-five Yuan? I can't even buy tickets with that.

234
00:18:13,140 --> 00:18:15,519
X-Xiaowen.

235
00:18:15,519 --> 00:18:18,979
You seem out of sorts today.

236
00:18:18,979 --> 00:18:21,071
Is there something on your mind?

237
00:18:21,860 --> 00:18:25,480
No, I just didn't sleep well last night.

238
00:18:26,200 --> 00:18:28,600
Is it because of Gao Yang?

239
00:18:33,939 --> 00:18:36,300
Did he... bully you?

240
00:18:37,720 --> 00:18:39,431
No.

241
00:18:41,599 --> 00:18:43,240
Don't worry.

242
00:18:43,240 --> 00:18:45,459
I can handle him.

243
00:18:45,459 --> 00:18:47,807
Let's go. Continue.

244
00:18:55,860 --> 00:18:57,478
Bye.

245
00:19:10,720 --> 00:19:13,809
[Don't waste your energy. Wait until I come home.]

246
00:19:13,809 --> 00:19:16,179
How dare you lock me in?

247
00:19:21,920 --> 00:19:23,774
It's too high.

248
00:19:42,280 --> 00:19:44,451
You little brat.

249
00:19:46,860 --> 00:19:49,000
What the hell are these?

250
00:20:17,390 --> 00:20:20,430
[Don't even think about running away, the rice is in the pot for you to eat.]

251
00:20:25,790 --> 00:20:28,599
Beibei, I'm locked in!

252
00:20:28,599 --> 00:20:32,639
Beibei, come save me now!

253
00:20:44,960 --> 00:20:46,040
Stop, stop.

254
00:20:46,040 --> 00:20:49,780
Beibei, you have to enjoy it and sing wholeheartedly.

255
00:20:49,780 --> 00:20:52,640
Look at Doudou, he just has the right feel.

256
00:20:52,640 --> 00:20:54,919
- Okay, let's do it again.
- Sing it nicely.

257
00:20:54,919 --> 00:20:57,720
Three, two, one.

258
00:21:12,800 --> 00:21:14,859
Bravo!

259
00:21:14,859 --> 00:21:17,420
Mom, I'm not singing anymore!

260
00:21:17,420 --> 00:21:20,000
What do you mean you're not singing? Put it on. Are you asking for a beating?

261
00:21:20,000 --> 00:21:22,799
I'm already a high school student. Why should I sing that?

262
00:21:22,799 --> 00:21:24,919
You... I'm sorry, Sir.

263
00:21:24,919 --> 00:21:28,019
Didn't the teacher tell you this is to build up your foundation?

264
00:21:28,019 --> 00:21:31,050
This is for you to develop a skill.

265
00:21:31,050 --> 00:21:33,520
Besides, we already paid the fees. We can't get a refund.

266
00:21:33,520 --> 00:21:36,300
Put it on. Go sing right now. Go on.

267
00:21:36,300 --> 00:21:37,820
Just develop his skill. I'm going home.

268
00:21:37,820 --> 00:21:39,540
What do you mean you're going home?

269
00:21:39,540 --> 00:21:43,880
Your dad is usually so busy at work. It's finally the weekend. Can't you let him get some sleep?

270
00:21:44,730 --> 00:21:46,079
Sister, come on.

271
00:21:46,079 --> 00:21:48,200
Wuli Gao Yang.

272
00:21:48,200 --> 00:21:50,240
Wuli Gao Gao Yang.

273
00:21:50,240 --> 00:21:52,159
- Gao Gao Yang. Wuli Gao Gao Yang.
- Mom!

274
00:21:52,159 --> 00:21:54,400
Wuli Gao Gao Yang.

275
00:21:54,400 --> 00:21:58,579
In three years, the Olympic Games will be held in Beijing.

276
00:21:58,579 --> 00:22:00,179
This is a major event for Beijing
[VICE-PRINCIPAL]

277
00:22:00,179 --> 00:22:02,839
and a major event for everyone in the entire country.

278
00:22:02,839 --> 00:22:07,540
Welcome, colleagues of the education field from various regions throughout the country.

279
00:22:07,540 --> 00:22:11,920
Let's strengthen our communication and anticipate the Olympic Games together.

280
00:22:17,350 --> 00:22:19,340
- Is it finished?
- It just started.

281
00:22:19,340 --> 00:22:21,284
Next up...

282
00:22:23,630 --> 00:22:28,340
Old Bin, can you not doze off during the meeting?

283
00:22:28,340 --> 00:22:29,680
Pull yourself together.

284
00:22:29,680 --> 00:22:32,531
I'm not. I'm reading the information.

285
00:22:33,070 --> 00:22:35,110
Don't say anything.

286
00:22:35,110 --> 00:22:38,159
Teachers from Beijing are looking at us.

287
00:22:39,040 --> 00:22:42,280
...follow the various relevant regulations in school,

288
00:22:42,280 --> 00:22:47,200
and do physical exams in the hospital to make sure the athletes' health is suitable to participate in the competition

289
00:22:47,200 --> 00:22:51,039
While participating athletes are studying in high school,

290
00:22:51,039 --> 00:22:55,200
they cannot participate in more than five championship games,

291
00:22:55,200 --> 00:22:58,019
no more than three championship games for junior college students.

292
00:22:58,019 --> 00:23:00,800
While they are in school, the amount of championship games...

293
00:23:00,800 --> 00:23:03,761
What are you doing now?

294
00:23:03,761 --> 00:23:06,060
It's an urgent matter. I have to make a call.

295
00:23:06,060 --> 00:23:08,097
Call after the meeting.

296
00:23:08,097 --> 00:23:10,660
- I need to poop.
- Hold it in.

297
00:23:14,340 --> 00:23:18,520
All participating athletes must be based on the school of the athletes...

298
00:23:18,550 --> 00:23:22,210
[With kind and beautiful words, it can bring warmth to your home]

299
00:23:44,310 --> 00:23:46,240
Isn't that Gao Bin's son?

300
00:23:46,240 --> 00:23:48,939
That boy is so naughty!

301
00:23:48,939 --> 00:23:50,740
Who is that?

302
00:23:50,740 --> 00:23:53,008
It's not the New Year yet.

303
00:23:54,410 --> 00:23:57,093
Gao Yang, what are you doing?

304
00:23:57,093 --> 00:23:58,860
Hurry, put the firecrackers away!

305
00:23:58,860 --> 00:24:01,340
What are you saying, Principal?

306
00:24:01,340 --> 00:24:03,440
Gao Yang, are you trying to revolt?

307
00:24:03,440 --> 00:24:06,859
Blame Gao Bin for bringing in a second son to bully me.

308
00:24:06,859 --> 00:24:09,860
Just you wait. I'm coming downstairs to punish you!

309
00:24:09,860 --> 00:24:12,580
That's great! Come downstairs now!

310
00:24:13,650 --> 00:24:15,540
Good thing Bin left me a spare key.

311
00:24:15,540 --> 00:24:18,019
Gao Yang, I'll punish you!

312
00:24:19,680 --> 00:24:22,389
Gao Yang!

313
00:24:22,389 --> 00:24:26,080
Principal! You're finally here, Principal!

314
00:24:26,080 --> 00:24:30,340
- W-What happened?
- I really have no other choice!

315
00:24:30,340 --> 00:24:32,720
There's no place for me in this house anymore!

316
00:24:32,720 --> 00:24:36,439
I can only go to Beijing to see my mom! Please give me some travel fare, Principal.

317
00:24:36,439 --> 00:24:37,820
- Sure, sure...
- What's wrong?

318
00:24:37,820 --> 00:24:40,653
My pants! My pants!

319
00:24:42,110 --> 00:24:43,939
Don't... don't bullsh*t me.

320
00:24:43,939 --> 00:24:46,299
You... you're always bullying your dad.

321
00:24:46,299 --> 00:24:48,459
What do you mean no place for you?

322
00:24:48,459 --> 00:24:50,140
Principal, you have no idea.

323
00:24:50,140 --> 00:24:53,379
Gao Bin brought a lackey home. He's only here for one day.

324
00:24:53,379 --> 00:24:56,380
Look at what a mess he made in the house!

325
00:24:56,380 --> 00:24:58,599
He even locked me in,

326
00:24:58,599 --> 00:25:02,740
starved me, and mentally abused me.

327
00:25:02,740 --> 00:25:06,859
Now, I'm already falling apart.

328
00:25:08,270 --> 00:25:10,114
Are you talking about Xiaowen?

329
00:25:10,870 --> 00:25:13,619
He's a good kid.

330
00:25:13,619 --> 00:25:17,139
Do you know that? Stop acting.

331
00:25:17,139 --> 00:25:20,059
He's a good kid? He's rotten to the core! Let me tell you, Principal.

332
00:25:20,059 --> 00:25:22,939
I will not be in the same house with him!

333
00:25:22,939 --> 00:25:24,840
You have to help me.

334
00:25:24,840 --> 00:25:27,699
I'm telling you, he will not be in the same house with you!

335
00:25:27,699 --> 00:25:29,119
Gao Yang, I'll tell you nicely.

336
00:25:29,119 --> 00:25:32,699
He's not like you. He has a unique identity.

337
00:25:32,699 --> 00:25:37,040
Treat him nicer. This time, I won't be biased toward you.

338
00:25:37,040 --> 00:25:41,299
Principal, what unique identity does he have?

339
00:25:41,299 --> 00:25:42,520
I...

340
00:25:42,520 --> 00:25:45,640
It's him! Principal, he's the one who bullies me every day!

341
00:25:45,640 --> 00:25:47,140
Get him!

342
00:25:47,140 --> 00:25:49,459
Principal Jin, why are you here?

343
00:25:49,459 --> 00:25:50,861
I...

344
00:25:51,630 --> 00:25:53,270
Let go!

345
00:25:54,980 --> 00:25:59,059
Xiaowen, I just reprimanded him for you.

346
00:25:59,059 --> 00:26:03,345
If Gao Yang acts like a jerk again, come upstairs to get me. I'll handle him.

347
00:26:03,345 --> 00:26:05,629
Wait, Old Jin,

348
00:26:05,629 --> 00:26:08,060
you're so biased.

349
00:26:08,060 --> 00:26:10,219
I'm... biased...

350
00:26:10,219 --> 00:26:12,300
You have a bias towards him too, you know?

351
00:26:12,300 --> 00:26:16,178
Stay out of trouble. I'll be watching you these days.

352
00:26:48,440 --> 00:26:50,940
Let's talk.

353
00:26:50,940 --> 00:26:55,122
There's nothing to talk about. I already told you. I won't be in the same house as you.

354
00:27:17,490 --> 00:27:19,010
What are you doing?

355
00:27:19,010 --> 00:27:20,440
Burn it up.

356
00:27:20,440 --> 00:27:23,439
You don't like me, right?

357
00:27:23,439 --> 00:27:24,739
Fine, I'll burn it.

358
00:27:24,739 --> 00:27:27,881
You think I'm afraid of you? I'll burn it all.

359
00:27:30,460 --> 00:27:32,325
I'll burn it all.

360
00:27:32,325 --> 00:27:37,540
Go ahead. I'm staying at your house anyway. If you burn them, I'll wear yours.

361
00:27:37,540 --> 00:27:39,580
Why are you so shameless?

362
00:27:39,580 --> 00:27:42,139
You're the shameless one.

363
00:27:42,139 --> 00:27:45,220
F*ck you! This is my house!

364
00:27:48,410 --> 00:27:51,520
This is my house. How dare you hit me?

365
00:27:52,670 --> 00:27:53,879
Gao Yang, let me tell you.

366
00:27:53,879 --> 00:27:57,199
I have Principal Jin's approval to go to No. 3 High School.

367
00:27:57,199 --> 00:27:58,879
I have Mr. Gao's approval to come to your house.

368
00:27:58,879 --> 00:28:01,275
I came to study for college. I don't owe you anything.

369
00:28:01,275 --> 00:28:05,300
Who the hell are you? Why are you so arrogant?

370
00:28:05,300 --> 00:28:06,900
It doesn't matter who I am.

371
00:28:06,900 --> 00:28:10,114
If you don't want to get beat up, just keep yourself in line.

372
00:28:20,010 --> 00:28:22,140
I know who you are.

373
00:28:22,140 --> 00:28:24,599
For evil guys like you,

374
00:28:24,599 --> 00:28:26,838
why would you keep your secrets in a backpack?

375
00:28:43,680 --> 00:28:45,259
Gao Yang, open the door!

376
00:28:45,259 --> 00:28:46,780
Aren't you tough?

377
00:28:46,780 --> 00:28:50,000
Didn't you lock me in? Didn't you hit me? Come on, come out!

378
00:28:50,000 --> 00:28:51,060
Wait till I get out there.

379
00:28:51,060 --> 00:28:54,460
What can you do when you come out? Stop bragging.

380
00:28:54,460 --> 00:28:57,760
You're here for Gao Bin. You're just an athlete, right?

381
00:28:57,760 --> 00:29:01,623
You went out so early in the morning. Are you a long-distance runner?

382
00:29:01,623 --> 00:29:03,559
Open the door!

383
00:29:04,380 --> 00:29:06,419
Is your l-leg okay?

384
00:29:06,419 --> 00:29:08,660
If you hurt your leg, you won't be able to run long-distance anymore.

385
00:29:08,660 --> 00:29:10,679
You won't get a good score.

386
00:29:10,679 --> 00:29:12,699
I'm warning you one last time. Open the door.

387
00:29:12,699 --> 00:29:17,020
Fine. Give me the money Gao Bin left you and I can think about it.

388
00:29:17,020 --> 00:29:19,469
You wish!

389
00:29:19,469 --> 00:29:22,040
Then stay in there.

390
00:29:22,040 --> 00:29:23,860
Coming to Gao Bin to improve your scores.

391
00:29:23,860 --> 00:29:25,340
I don't know what you're thinking.

392
00:29:25,340 --> 00:29:27,585
You and him are two good-for-nothings.

393
00:29:33,350 --> 00:29:37,040
Gao Yang, you won't be able to keep me inside.

394
00:29:37,790 --> 00:29:39,660
What a tough guy.

395
00:29:39,660 --> 00:29:41,540
Jump out the window then.

396
00:29:41,540 --> 00:29:44,219
Anyway, I'm leaving. Bye.

397
00:29:57,870 --> 00:30:00,800
Sir, keep this orange on Gao Bin's tab.

398
00:30:02,179 --> 00:30:03,868
Gao Yang!

399
00:30:05,699 --> 00:30:07,240
Why? You won't give in?

400
00:30:07,240 --> 00:30:08,820
Come downstairs then.

401
00:30:08,820 --> 00:30:11,119
I'll give you a ten-minute head start. You can run first.

402
00:30:11,119 --> 00:30:13,040
Ten minutes? Stop bragging.

403
00:30:13,040 --> 00:30:16,220
When you come downstairs, I'll be in Tiananmen already.

404
00:30:25,879 --> 00:30:28,620
What Ms. An? I'm looking for Anna.

405
00:30:29,780 --> 00:30:32,960
Who am I? I'm her ex-husband.

406
00:30:32,960 --> 00:30:34,577
Bin.

407
00:30:35,792 --> 00:30:37,319
I don't care if she's busy.

408
00:30:37,319 --> 00:30:39,919
I have to see her today.

409
00:30:40,620 --> 00:30:43,480
A project? What project is more important than her son?

410
00:30:43,480 --> 00:30:46,240
- This is...
- What are you doing?

411
00:30:46,240 --> 00:30:48,280
Go get the material.

412
00:30:48,280 --> 00:30:50,760
You have to write a report when you go back.

413
00:30:50,760 --> 00:30:52,860
So absent-minded.

414
00:30:54,060 --> 00:30:55,319
Hello?

415
00:30:55,319 --> 00:30:56,680
Where should we meet?

416
00:30:56,680 --> 00:30:58,499
Say it again.

417
00:30:59,720 --> 00:31:02,760
Sir, the regulations for this sports event is not the same.

418
00:31:02,760 --> 00:31:05,319
Please take a closer look and see if your school can cooperate.

419
00:31:05,319 --> 00:31:06,980
Okay.

420
00:31:06,980 --> 00:31:09,620
Sir, please sign here.

421
00:31:12,920 --> 00:31:14,280
[Gao Bin]

422
00:31:14,280 --> 00:31:15,705
[Jenny's Salon]

423
00:31:15,705 --> 00:31:18,439
Don't miss the great deal.
[Jenny's Salon]

424
00:31:18,439 --> 00:31:22,739
Jenny's Salon will give you confidence and a nice look.

425
00:31:22,739 --> 00:31:25,699
Haircuts, haircuts.

426
00:31:26,340 --> 00:31:29,319
Jenny's Salon, famous throughout the world.

427
00:31:29,319 --> 00:31:32,900
Best in washes, haircuts, blow-dries, and perms.

428
00:31:32,900 --> 00:31:34,760
Haircuts, haircuts.

429
00:31:34,760 --> 00:31:36,820
Can't you speak louder?

430
00:31:36,820 --> 00:31:38,079
You haven't eaten yet?

431
00:31:38,079 --> 00:31:40,299
Isn't this your business too?

432
00:31:40,299 --> 00:31:43,079
You sing so loud every day.

433
00:31:43,079 --> 00:31:45,380
Yell it out, louder!

434
00:31:46,520 --> 00:31:49,599
Rely on the mountain and the mountain collapses. Rely on the river and the river dries out.

435
00:31:49,599 --> 00:31:51,939
Watch the chicken and the chicken dies. Watch the dog and the dog flips over.

436
00:31:51,939 --> 00:31:55,720
Old Jin, I can't rely on anyone, right?

437
00:31:55,720 --> 00:31:58,580
Dezhu, don't criticize him so much.

438
00:31:58,580 --> 00:32:00,499
Jiabao is already a sophomore in high school.

439
00:32:00,499 --> 00:32:02,879
Don't let him pass out so many fliers.

440
00:32:02,879 --> 00:32:05,300
His studies are the most important.

441
00:32:05,880 --> 00:32:09,340
His mind isn't focused on his studies at all.

442
00:32:09,340 --> 00:32:10,920
All he does is sing those stupid songs.

443
00:32:10,920 --> 00:32:13,080
It's not that easy to make a living by singing.

444
00:32:13,080 --> 00:32:16,520
If singing can make you get rich, why would I run this salon?

445
00:32:16,520 --> 00:32:19,740
I would just keep doing the dance opera.

446
00:32:19,740 --> 00:32:21,760
You can get rich by singing dance operas too.

447
00:32:21,760 --> 00:32:23,680
You just didn't persist, you know?

448
00:32:23,680 --> 00:32:25,040
Persist for what?

449
00:32:25,040 --> 00:32:29,179
Besides, it's good that the boy has a dream.

450
00:32:29,179 --> 00:32:33,419
It is good to have a dream. But I still think we should be more realistic. Am I right, Old Jin?

451
00:32:33,419 --> 00:32:37,660
Over the years, you're the one I admire the most.

452
00:32:37,660 --> 00:32:40,440
Look, you're here to shave your beard so early in the morning.

453
00:32:40,440 --> 00:32:42,380
Why are you so diligent?

454
00:32:42,380 --> 00:32:45,300
No wonder you're the principal, right?

455
00:32:45,300 --> 00:32:46,960
Do you think I want to?

456
00:32:46,960 --> 00:32:48,692
Gao Yang woke me up.

457
00:32:48,692 --> 00:32:52,431
What happened? Bin didn't keep him in line?

458
00:32:52,431 --> 00:32:54,219
Don't mention it.

459
00:32:54,219 --> 00:32:56,000
Bin went on a business trip.

460
00:32:56,000 --> 00:32:59,630
He said he needs to talk to Anna about something.

461
00:33:01,014 --> 00:33:03,200
He just doesn't want Gao Yang to go to Beijing.

462
00:33:03,200 --> 00:33:04,881
You know?

463
00:33:05,539 --> 00:33:09,519
I told him to communicate with the boy nicely.

464
00:33:09,519 --> 00:33:13,179
Don't always beat him or argue with him.

465
00:33:13,179 --> 00:33:15,159
You have no idea, Old Jin.

466
00:33:15,159 --> 00:33:17,219
Boys at their age...

467
00:33:17,219 --> 00:33:19,559
Jiabao is very assertive.
- Jiabao. Jiabao!

468
00:33:20,400 --> 00:33:22,060
Just take my child as an example.

469
00:33:22,060 --> 00:33:26,059
We won't let him sing but he just has to sing. We can't stop him.

470
00:33:26,059 --> 00:33:28,442
Can't do anything about it.

471
00:33:29,451 --> 00:33:30,497
What are you doing?

472
00:33:30,497 --> 00:33:36,120
Dezhu, you and Bin, both of you have to be patient with your children.

473
00:33:36,120 --> 00:33:39,140
All right, stop lecturing anyone you can find.

474
00:33:39,140 --> 00:33:41,159
I'm just saying.

475
00:33:47,800 --> 00:33:49,900
Gao Yang is here?

476
00:33:50,919 --> 00:33:52,060
Mom, here you go.

477
00:33:52,060 --> 00:33:56,380
These boys, they ran so fast. Old Jin is here too?

478
00:33:56,380 --> 00:33:57,799
What did you do to him?

479
00:33:57,799 --> 00:34:00,200
- Hurry, take care of it!
- He moved!

480
00:34:00,200 --> 00:34:01,959
Take care of this! Hurry!

481
00:34:01,959 --> 00:34:04,158
Hurry, hurry. Go get a band-aid!

482
00:34:44,499 --> 00:34:46,439
Hurry up.

483
00:34:49,059 --> 00:34:51,059
Don't dilly dally.

484
00:34:57,619 --> 00:35:01,679
With your pool skills, how can you call yourself a bad student?

485
00:35:02,680 --> 00:35:04,240
Cherish this.

486
00:35:04,240 --> 00:35:06,834
You don't have a chance to play with me anymore.

487
00:35:07,499 --> 00:35:10,259
Why? You're still going to Beijing?

488
00:35:10,259 --> 00:35:12,339
I have to this time.

489
00:35:12,339 --> 00:35:14,680
I can't stay home anymore.

490
00:35:17,931 --> 00:35:20,240
- What are you doing?
- Lend me some money.

491
00:35:20,240 --> 00:35:23,300
No, I won't. I knew you wouldn't treat me to pool for nothing.

492
00:35:23,300 --> 00:35:25,039
- Hurry up.
- I'm not lending it to you.

493
00:35:25,039 --> 00:35:26,900
- Hurry up!
- I have use for it.

494
00:35:26,900 --> 00:35:28,519
What do you need it for?

495
00:35:28,519 --> 00:35:31,479
If you don't lend them to me, you'll end up using them to buy snacks for Beibei.

496
00:35:31,479 --> 00:35:32,740
I'll tell my mom to pay you back when I get to Beijing.

497
00:35:32,740 --> 00:35:35,440
Dawei is here.

498
00:35:35,440 --> 00:35:37,880
- What's going on?
- Let's go. Let's go. Go, go, go.

499
00:35:37,880 --> 00:35:39,359
- It's not time yet.
- Go.

500
00:35:39,359 --> 00:35:40,639
What are you looking for? I'll help you.

501
00:35:40,639 --> 00:35:42,039
- Let's go.
- Where are you going?

502
00:35:42,039 --> 00:35:44,085
- Get down.
- What are you looking for?

503
00:35:46,079 --> 00:35:48,199
Go, go, go.

504
00:35:58,340 --> 00:35:59,979
Where's my black eight?

505
00:35:59,979 --> 00:36:02,124
Where did my black eight go?

506
00:36:02,124 --> 00:36:04,700
- It's over there.
- That's right.

507
00:36:04,700 --> 00:36:06,660
- Time's up?
- Sure, sure.

508
00:36:06,660 --> 00:36:08,332
Let's go.

509
00:36:11,479 --> 00:36:13,999
Aren't you Zhang Long and Zhao Hu?

510
00:36:15,419 --> 00:36:17,000
You're all here.

511
00:36:17,000 --> 00:36:20,268
What a coincidence, Brother Dawei. You're here to play pool?

512
00:36:23,039 --> 00:36:27,380
Gao Yang, you're not even greeting me now?

513
00:36:27,380 --> 00:36:29,319
Wait, are we familiar with each other?

514
00:36:29,319 --> 00:36:32,399
Here's the thing. I'm focused on my studies now.

515
00:36:32,399 --> 00:36:35,158
We're... not going down the same path.

516
00:36:35,820 --> 00:36:38,200
What path am I taking?

517
00:36:38,200 --> 00:36:40,580
- To be a gang leader.
- That's right.

518
00:36:40,580 --> 00:36:42,120
Aren't you the leader of No. 3 High School?

519
00:36:42,120 --> 00:36:45,879
Well, I won't keep you from outshining everyone.

520
00:36:45,879 --> 00:36:48,842
Enjoy the game. We're leaving now.

521
00:36:57,220 --> 00:36:59,298
Hurry, hurry.

522
00:36:59,298 --> 00:37:00,960
Take the shortcut.

523
00:37:00,960 --> 00:37:02,240
Why is Dong Dawei always coming after you?

524
00:37:02,240 --> 00:37:03,640
How did you offend him?

525
00:37:03,640 --> 00:37:05,540
If it's too much to handle, just apologize. You can't go on like this.

526
00:37:05,540 --> 00:37:07,412
It's too late.

527
00:37:45,806 --> 00:37:51,861
♫  I know the direction of dawn  ♫

528
00:37:51,861 --> 00:37:59,326
♫  It's right in front of me, waiting for me to shine  ♫

529
00:37:59,326 --> 00:38:05,250
♫  The starlight that shines alone the way  ♫

530
00:38:05,250 --> 00:38:11,316
♫  Accompanying me on my adventure, packing my dreams in my heart  ♫

531
00:38:11,316 --> 00:38:17,954
♫  I don't fear the rough journey ahead, I will no longer run away  ♫

532
00:38:17,954 --> 00:38:23,548
♫  Maybe I'm not destined for the hardship of this journey  ♫

533
00:38:23,548 --> 00:38:27,435
♫  And chase after the longing in my heart  ♫

534
00:38:27,435 --> 00:38:30,883
♫  Let set sail on your dreams  ♫

535
00:38:30,883 --> 00:38:34,278
♫  Let's not have any regrets in our youth  ♫

536
00:38:34,278 --> 00:38:40,946
♫  Even if you stumble and fall, you'll have me by your side  ♫

537
00:38:40,946 --> 00:38:44,149
♫  Let's find the answer through the madness  ♫

538
00:38:44,149 --> 00:38:48,361
♫  Let's have courage to ride the waves and billows  ♫

539
00:38:48,361 --> 00:38:52,081
♫  With my wings, I'll fly us to the future  ♫

540
00:38:52,081 --> 00:38:58,941
♫  And step forward into the future without fear of sorrow  ♫
